  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ARE YOU THE KING OF TRIVIA?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself in Trivia King.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trivia has never been so much fun. Play on your own in Single Player Mode, or host a trivia night with friends and family in Party Mode (up to 4 players). Choose a category and answer thousands of multiple-choice questions. Family-friendly and easy to pick up—perfect for quick sessions or longer game nights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Includes 8 popular categories:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>American Trivia</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Movies and TV</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Entertainment and Music</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>History</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Geography</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Literature</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Science</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Food</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single Player Mode</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Party Mode (Up to 4 Players)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Thousands of multiple-choice questions</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Perfect for group trivia nights</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quick, pick-up-and-play sessions</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Family-friendly fun for all ages</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gamepad support</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So what are you waiting for? Prove you're the King of Trivia (or Queen)!</p>",
